        <div class="info-who-grid">
            <div  class="info-who-text">
                <h2 data-aos="fade-down-right">THE TEAM</h2>
                <p data-aos="fade-right"> At the heart of our team lies a deep passion for Tasmania's untamed beauty and an unwavering respect for its breathtaking landscapes. We are driven by a shared vision: to shine a spotlight on The Abels, Tasmania’s majestic mountain peaks, and inspire others to discover and cherish their extraordinary wonder. Together, we are committed to raising awareness of The Abels, ensuring their significance is recognized and celebrated by adventurers and nature lovers alike.</p><br>
                <p data-aos="fade-up-right">Through our collaboration with Tourism Tasmania, we aim to promote sustainable tourism, respect for the environment, and a deeper connection to nature. Our mission is to celebrate The Abels, making these extraordinary peaks accessible to a global audience while preserving the natural beauty that makes Tasmania so special.</p>
            </div>
            <div data-aos="zoom-in" class="info-who-img">
                <img src="/img/the-team.jpeg" alt="image of Tas Peaks team">
                <a class="come-say-hi-btn buttonB" href="#">Drop us a line</a>
            </div>


        </div>

    </div>
</secion>
